{"word":"G2334 - θεωρέω - theōréō - theh-o-reh'-o - Behold","slug":"G2334","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θεωρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>theōréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>theh-o-reh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Behold"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x03C9;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - theo&#x0304;reo&#x0304;</b> - <i>theh-o-reh'-o</i><p/>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2300\">G2300</a> (perhaps by adverb of <a href=\"#/G3708\">G3708</a>); to <i>be a spectator</i> of, that is, <i>discern</i>, (literally, figuratively [<i>experience</i>] or intensively [<i>acknowledge</i>]): - behold, consider, look on, perceive, see. Compare <a href=\"#/G3700\">G3700</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2300\">G2300</a>, <a href=\"#/G2529\">G2529</a>, <a href=\"#/G3705\">G3705</a>, <a href=\"#/G3706\">G3706</a>, <a href=\"#/G3707\">G3707</a>, <a href=\"#/G3708\">G3708</a>, <a href=\"#/G4308\">G4308</a>, <a href=\"#/G517\">G517</a>"}]}